{
  "texts": [
    "For all labels and annotators, we find a global inter-annotator agreement score (Krippendorff's alpha) of 0.3064.",
    "In this section, we provide symptom distribution analysis for D2S and DSD-Clinician-Tweets datasets.",
    "DSD-Clinician-Tweets dataset contains 1500 tweets.",
    "We then create a clean subset of this dataset which holds clinicians' annotations and only tweets with depression symptoms, which we call DSD-Clinician-Tweets-Original (further detail is in Sect. 4.2.1).",
    "For D2S, we have 1584 tweets with different depression symptom labels."
  ]
}